[2]
Date: Thu 26 Jan 2012
Source: Le Republicain Lorrain [in French, machine trans., summ. edited]
http://www.republicain-lorrain.fr/actualite/2012/01/26/premiers-cas


The 1st [2 suspected cases] of SBV [Schmallenberg virus] have been recorded in sheep in Moselle and Meurthe-et-Moselle. Additional suspected cases are being analysed.

